Mel spectrogram interpolation¶

Loop until the spectrogram is sufficiently close to the target spectrogram:

  • $\mathbf{x} \gets \text{WaveNet}(\text{spectrogram})$

  • $\text{spectrogram} \gets \mu \cdot (\text{spectrogram of $\mathbf{x}$}) + (1 - \mu) \cdot (\text{target spectrogram})$
